### Register an OAuth client
POST http://localhost:4000/clients/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Demo App",
    "redirectUris": ["http://localhost:3000/callback"],
    "allowedScopes": ["openid", "profile", "email"],
    "appUrl": "http://localhost:3000"
}

### Register - minimal (openid only)
POST http://localhost:4000/clients/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Minimal Client",
    "redirectUris": ["http://localhost:3000/callback"],
    "allowedScopes": ["openid"]
}

### Register - missing openid scope (should fail with 400)
POST http://localhost:4000/clients/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Bad Client",
    "redirectUris": ["http://localhost:3000/callback"],
    "allowedScopes": ["profile", "email"]
}

### Register - invalid redirect URI (should fail with 400)
POST http://localhost:4000/clients/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Bad URI Client",
    "redirectUris": ["not-a-url"],
    "allowedScopes": ["openid"]
}
